1
00:01:09,080 --> 00:01:09,800
Wait.

2
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:17,840
What's wrong, Zhang?

3
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,680
Bring us

4
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:21,340
some pork knuckles tomorrow.

5
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:23,330
It's the best to go with the drinks.

6
00:01:24,039 --> 00:01:24,800
No problem.

7
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:25,720
Will do.

8
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:26,880
Go.

9
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:27,690
I'm leaving.

10
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:31,840
How is it?

11
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:33,090
I've changed it.

12
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:34,360
Great. Hurry up.

13
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,000
Quick, go.

14
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:40,880
Come.

15
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:41,440
Uncle,

16
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,120
Lao Lin.

17
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:42,800
Mr. Qin,

18
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,440
Dad.

19
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:45,120
How did your leg get injured?

20
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:45,759
I'm fine.

21
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:47,720
It's good enough that you came back alive.

22
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,840
Brother, go get the medicine quickly.

23
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,360
Okay.

24
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:51,280
Yamada and Luo Wang,

25
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,340
these two animals.

26
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,360
Sooner or later, I will

27
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,039
chop them up into pieces

28
00:01:54,039 --> 00:01:55,520
and throw them into the sea to feed the fish.

29
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:56,120
This time,

30
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:58,080
it's all thanks to Jiadong's idea.

31
00:01:58,080 --> 00:01:59,160
I really didn't expect

32
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,600
we could rescue you so quickly.

33
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:01,120
Yeah.

34
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:02,240
Brother Jiadong

35
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:03,800
is smart, brave, and careful.

36
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,200
Combined with Brother Mingshu's skills,

37
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,600
it really opened my eyes.

38
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,530
Mr. Qin, Brother Zheng,

39
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,419
you flatter me.

40
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,800
It's just that this matter

41
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,960
has implicated Brother Zheng.

42
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,000
He will be exposed soon.

43
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,760
Please hurry and send him out of the city, Mr. Qin.

44
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:15,200
Okay.

45
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:16,940
It doesn't matter.

46
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,960
If it weren't for making a living,

47
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:18,560
I wouldn't be willing

48
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:20,490
to work for a scumbag like Luo Wang.

49
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,040
Being able to help you before leaving,

50
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:22,720
it's worth it.

51
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,579
Brother Zheng,

52
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:25,040
thank you very much.

53
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:25,370
Okay.

54
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:25,960
We can talk about gratitude

55
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:26,640
later.

56
00:02:27,079 --> 00:02:28,400
I'll see Zheng Yi out first.

57
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,060
Sorry to trouble you, Mr. Qin.

58
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:37,490
Wangshu, the medicine.

59
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,040
Okay.

60
00:02:39,079 --> 00:02:39,480
Dad,

61
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,480
let me apply the medicine for you.

62
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:42,040
Okay.

63
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:45,200
Easy.

64
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:50,600
I heard

65
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:54,000
you didn't get my permission

66
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,180
before marrying my daughter.

67
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,440
Dad.

68
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,360
What are you waiting for?

69
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:07,570
Father-in-law, please accept my bow.

70
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:23,640
Old Lin.

71
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,340
I'll give you one more chance.

72
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,170
Don't hold out anymore.

73
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:32,480
As long as you lure Chen Jiadong out

74
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,850
and marry Wangshu to me,

75
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:39,880
I can let you leave alive.

76
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:42,810
How about it?

77
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,000
I'm talking to you.

78
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:44,800
Do you hear me?

79
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:48,320
Someone!

80
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:50,600
Someone!

81
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:54,680
Sheriff.

82
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,120
Open the door!

83
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:00,760
Open the door!

84
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:03,960
Hurry up.

85
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,480
Old Lin.

86
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:22,320
Yamada.

87
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:26,640
Yamada.

88
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:31,440
Bastard.

89
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:32,840
What's going on?

90
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,200
Idiots.

91
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:39,490
This is completely stupid.

92
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,159
President.

93
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:43,000
I have severely

94
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,200
punished those cops.

95
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:45,520
But there's one thing

96
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,980
I still don't understand.

97
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:48,480
You were perfectly fine.

98
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:49,600
How did they

99
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,800
suddenly arrest you?

100
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:52,520
Shut up.

101
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:55,250
It's all your fault, you idiot,

102
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,620
for ruining my plan

103
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:57,640
completely.

104
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,650
Don't shoot yet.

105
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,300
I've investigated it.

106
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:02,000
There's a cop named Zheng Yi.

107
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,000
He delivers food,

108
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:05,000
and he collaborated with those people.

109
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:07,000
Those people really deserve to die.

110
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,620
But isn't Chen Jiadong

111
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,280
the one who deserves it most?

112
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,080
That Zheng Yi,

113
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:16,760
where is he?

114
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:19,000
I've already sent someone to catch him.

115
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:19,730
Don't worry.

116
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,840
I'll definitely bring him back

117
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,300
for you to vent your anger.

118
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,280
Luo Wang,

119
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,220
I'll give you one more chance.

120
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:33,159
Take your men immediately

121
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:36,240
under the pretext of rescuing death row inmates

122
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,400
and intending to rebel against

123
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:38,800
the Malayan government.

124
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,800
Go and arrest

125
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,840
everyone in the Chinese Chamber of Commerce.

126
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:45,800
Wh-what?

127
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,360
Everyone?

128
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:48,520
I said everyone.

129
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:49,800
Everyone.

130
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:51,360
Force them

131
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:53,300
to hand over Chen Jiadong.

132
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,280
I want to see

133
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:58,040
if these Chinese

134
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,000
are so united

135
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:03,620
that they are willing to die together for Chen Jiadong.

136
00:06:03,840 --> 00:06:04,520
Boss.

137
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:07,140
But with such a big commotion,

138
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:08,600
the Malayan government

139
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,440
and Songkan,

140
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,900
they won't just ignore it.

141
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,520
What is Songkan?

142
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:18,240
I have already prepared

143
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,240
to pressure the Malayan government

144
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,690
to dismiss Songkan.

145
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,660
Inspector Luo,

146
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,480
congratulations.

147
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:30,700
You are about to become

148
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:33,820
the chief of the Malayan Police Department.

149
00:06:39,159 --> 00:06:40,840
Thank you, President Yamada,

150
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:41,640
and the Great Japanese Empire,

151
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:42,770
for cultivating me.

152
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:43,500
I, Luo Wang,

153
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:45,680
will certainly not disappoint you

154
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,880
and will do my utmost.

155
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:48,720
Very well.

156
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,520
Director Luo,

157
00:06:54,159 --> 00:06:55,490
don't let me down again,

158
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,040
or else.

159
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:57,920
Rest assured.

160
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:00,480
If I can't handle this properly,

161
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:01,840
you can shoot me.

162
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:04,640
Luo Wang and Yamada

163
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:05,640
have suffered a big setback,

164
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:07,170
they won't let it go easily.

165
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,680
We should find a way to get you out

166
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:11,420
of Malaya as soon as possible.

167
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:13,360
If last time the three of us

168
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:14,360
escaped with the evidence

169
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,640
facing a two-front siege,

170
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:17,900
this time we're surrounded on all sides.

171
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,240
Jiadong is right.

172
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:21,720
However, Mr. Qin,

173
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:24,050
I can't just leave like this

174
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:25,810
and leave all the trouble to you

175
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,600
and the chamber of commerce.

176
00:07:28,520 --> 00:07:29,650
What about Songkan?

177
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,480
He collects protection fees

178
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,600
from our Chinese chamber of commerce

179
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:33,640
every month.

180
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:35,080
Now is the time for him

181
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:36,080
to do his part.

182
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:38,120
Use him to suppress Luo Wang,

183
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,200
while we

184
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:41,409
send Old Lin and the three kids out.

185
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:44,000
I haven't had time to tell you.

186
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:44,760
Previously, Songkan

187
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:46,159
took bribes from Yamada.

188
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:47,570
But early this morning,

189
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,400
due to pressure from the Japanese,

190
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,730
Songkan was dismissed.

191
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,020
The new chief of police

192
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:52,840
is Luo Wang.

193
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,200
We're in trouble now.

194
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,280
What about the Malayan government?

195
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:58,159
Are they just letting the Japanese

196
00:07:58,159 --> 00:07:59,159
manipulate them like this?

197
00:07:59,159 --> 00:08:00,640
I was also very surprised.

198
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,280
It seems

199
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:04,480
the Japanese influence in Malaya

200
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,010
is beyond our imagination.

201
00:08:06,760 --> 00:08:07,440
Right now,

202
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,730
most of our country has fallen,

203
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,320
and the Japanese in Southeast Asia

204
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,780
are also running rampant.

205
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,480
Meanwhile, the Malayan government

206
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:16,720
is cowering,

207
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,930
playing it safe.

208
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:20,000
Damn Luo Wang.

209
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:21,640
I really want to put a sack over his head at night

210
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:22,700
and finish him off.

211
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,920
Wangshu makes sense.

212
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:30,600
Luo Wang might be our breakthrough.

213
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:32,520
No matter how arrogant Yamada is,

214
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:33,559
he still needs the help of Luo Wang,

215
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:35,280
the local police chief.

216
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,880
If Luo Wang is killed,

217
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,640
it's like cutting off one of his arms.

218
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:39,640
If we can make

219
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,600
a rift between them,

220
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:42,039
wouldn't that be even better?

221
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:43,700
That's easier said than done.

222
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,320
Mr. Qin.

223
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:47,340
This is bad.

224
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:48,480
Luo Wang brought the police

225
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:50,040
and surrounded us.

226
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,320
He is so arrogant.

227
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:52,420
I'll go see him.

228
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,100
I'll go too.

229
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:55,080
Stay here and don't move.

230
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,480
Mr. Zhao is right.

231
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:59,000
No matter what happens outside,

232
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,000
you must not move.

233
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,160
He will definitely find a way

234
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,090
to force you out.

235
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,940
As long as you stay hidden.

236
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,980
He won't dare to do anything to me.

237
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,920
We are in trouble now.

238
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:13,360
Luo Wang dared to say

239
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,800
he'd arrest the entire Chinese Chamber of Commerce.

240
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:16,260
This must be Japan's idea.

241
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:18,900
His confidence comes from the Japanese.

242
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,680
What do we do now?

243
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,800
I'll go check on them.

244
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:23,880
Wangshu,

245
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,960
take Dad inside first

246
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,690
and wait for Brother Mingshu to come back.

247
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,770
I'll go with you.

248
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:31,060
I'm worried about you.

249
00:09:34,880 --> 00:09:35,440
Luo Wang.

250
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,560
You are too insolent.

251
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:42,180
How dare you surround the Chinese Chamber of Commerce!

252
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:43,360
Mr. Qin.

253
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:47,080
By order of the Malayan government,

254
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:49,240
the Chinese Chamber of Commerce is suspected of hijacking a death row inmate

255
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,880
and rebelling against the government.

256
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:51,810
It is now decided

257
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,760
to shut down the Chinese Chamber of Commerce.

258
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:54,320
Everyone

259
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,000
will be arrested pending trial.

260
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:56,760
Insolent!

261
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,450
If you have the guts,

262
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,440
tell the Malayan government officials

263
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,170
to talk to me.

264
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:01,240
Luo Wang.

265
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:04,480
Hijacking a death row inmate and rebelling against the government

266
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:06,200
is a huge crime.

267
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:08,320
What evidence do you have?

268
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,600
The death row inmate, Lin Zhongzheng,

269
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:12,280
is closely related to your Mr. Qin,

270
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:13,960
and is also a member of your Chamber of Commerce.

271
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,160
That is the evidence.

272
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,640
This Luo Wang is indeed up to no good.

273
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:21,280
Luo Wang.

274
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,600
You neglected your duty

275
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:24,120
and failed to watch the prisoner.

276
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,240
Now you want to pin

277
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,480
the blame on us.

278
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:28,080
Chinese businesses account for

279
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,480
more than half of Malaya.

280
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:30,720
I'd like to see you try.

281
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,000
If there's any evidence,

282
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,530
I'll find out once I search.

283
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:35,960
Take everyone back.

284
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:37,700
If anyone resists,

285
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:38,840
shoot them.

286
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:40,680
Chief,

287
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,040
what about Mr. Qin?

288
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:44,100
I don't care if his name is Qin or Zhao.

289
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:46,800
There's only the wanted criminal I'm after here.

290
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:48,260
Anyone who dares to resist

291
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:50,460
will be killed without mercy.

292
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:53,520
Mr. Qin,

293
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,880
I'll give you one chance.

294
00:10:56,520 --> 00:10:57,980
Hand over Lin Zhongzheng,

295
